<p>I&rsquo;m <em>Pavel Iosad</em>, and I'm a Lecturer in Theoretical Phonology in the department of <a href="http://www.lel.ed.ac.uk">Linguistics and English Language</a> at the <a href="http://www.ed.ac.uk">University of Edinburgh</a>. &para; You can always go to the <a href="http://anghyflawn.github.io">start page</a> to learn more.</p>
